    <stitle>VT 275 Engine Service Manual - Dual Turbocharger and Exhaust Tubing - Installation - Turbocharger and
        Exhaust Tubing Torque Sequence
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc graphiccount="6">
        <title>Turbocharger and Exhaust Tubing Torque Sequence</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Make sure all bolts, nuts and clamps are already in place and hand tight. Torque turbocharger and
                    tubing related hardware in the following order:
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <figure id="f3000333" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figj15/J15031.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Torquing the three turbocharger mounting bolts</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Torque the three turbocharger mounting bolts (M8 x 30) to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_311.xml" xrefid="S300GTG">Standard Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f3000334" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figj15/J15032.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Torquing the exhaust tube assembly at manifold</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten bolts / nuts (M8 x 60) on each side of the exhaust tube assembly incrementally
                (alternating between bolts), by using the following
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_53.xml" xrefid="E30003B">Special Torque</hotlnk>
                values:
            </para>
            <seqlist>
                <item>
                    <para>Tighten exhaust tube bolts to &#8531; published torque value.</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Tighten exhaust tube bolts to &#8532; published torque value.</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Tighten exhaust tube bolts to full published torque value.</para>
                </item>
            </seqlist>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f3000333.5" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figj14/J14010.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Torquing the exhaust tube assembly at EGR cooler</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten exhaust tube V-band clamp at EGR cooler to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_53.xml" xrefid="E30003B">Special Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f3000335" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figj15/J15005.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Torquing the exhaust tube assembly at turbocharger inlet</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Torque each of the four turbocharger exhaust tube assembly bolts (M10 x 25) to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_53.xml" xrefid="E30003B">Special Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f3000336" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figj15/J15009.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Torquing the crossover tube clamp</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Torque the crossover tube clamp to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_53.xml" xrefid="E30003B">Special Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f3000337" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figj15/J15033.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Torquing the turbine mating clamp</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Verify alignment marks are together, then torque the turbine mating clamp to the
                <hotlnk document="eges3001_53.xml" xrefid="E30003B">Special Torque</hotlnk>.
            </para>
        </step1>
